<Issue id="31806" key="IS-812" number="812" project="10401" reporter="douglaswightman" assignee="zhigunenko.dsr" creator="douglaswightman" type="10004" summary="libnullpay fees API sequence needs independent signing" priority="3" resolution="10000" status="10001" created="2018-07-11 19:19:41.0" updated="2018-08-03 09:00:29.0" resolutiondate="2018-08-03 09:00:29.0" votes="0" watches="3" workflowId="51455"> <description><! CDATA When paying fees using libnullpay the following API sequence is used:  1) build_request (NYM, SCHEMA, CRED_DEF for example)  2) indy_add_request_fees  3) indy_sign_and_submit_request  However, the signing of the fees and the signing of the request should be independent.  The following API sequence is used in libsovtoken and should be copied by libnullpay:  1) build_request (NYM, SCHEMA, CRED_DEF for example)  2) indy_sign_request  3) indy_add_request_fees  4) indy_submit_request  ></description> </Issue>
